1. vagrant up
2. vagrant ssh
3. wget https://collectd.org/files/collectd-5.5.0.tar.bz2    #collectd sources
4. ./configure
5. make all install
6. Installation can be found under /opt/collectd
7. Copy the collectd.conf file from this repo to /opt/collectd/etc. This enables logging to logs/collectd.log and also adds collected metrics to this log
8. mkdir /opt/collectd/logs 
9. sbin/collectd
 
#will automate the collectd setup soon
